descriptionNullable: Time series analysis deals with time series based data to extract patterns for predictions and other characteristics of the data. It uses a model for forecasting future values in a small time frame based on previous observations. It is widely used for non-stationary data, such as economic data, weather data, stock prices, and retail sales forecasting.
